posting_body: ['Mike Miller', '| The Apartment Resource |', 'show contact info', 'Modern Elegance, Amenities Galore!', 'Kellogg Blvd, St. Paul, MN', '$1299/month', 'Bedrooms: 1   Bathrooms:  1', 'Sq Footage 555', 'Parking: $125/Garage Parking', 'Pet Policy: Cats & Dogs OK', 'Deposit $400', 'Premium Lifestyle!', ' Extraordinary Apartment Homes!', ' A Cut Above The Rest!', 'Life is about choices.', 'This one is easy.', 'Choose a sophisticated & sustainable lifestyle in the heart of the city.', 'Where Smart homes meet urban walkability, historic setting, dynamic views, and trendsetting design.', 'Select from a wide variety of 1 & 2 bedroom single level apartments, or 2-story Mezzanine level lofts.', 'Offering big style and amenity rich living in a smaller, quaint historic building.', 'Prices and availability are subject to change.', 'Photos may not represent exact unit.', 'COMMUNITY AMENITIES', 'Community Car', 'Walkable neighborhood with restaurants, services, shops and entertainment venues', 'Club quality fitness center with yoga studio, spin bikes, fitness plans and free weight equipment', 'Mingle room featuring fireplace and cozy gathering nooks', 'Rooftop terrace with grilling lounge', 'Game & entertainment lounge', 'Dog friendly with paw spa & private dog park', 'Bike storage and repair station', 'Package acceptance & storage room', 'On-Site Maintenance Available 24/7', 'Elevator', 'Business Center', 'Extra Storage', 'APARTMENT AMENITIES', 'In-Unit Washer/Dryer', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Walk-In Closets', 'Kitchen Island', 'Balcony*', 'Double Oven*', 'Wine Fridge*', '*In Select Units', 'Contact:', 'Mike Miller | The Apartment Resource |', 'show contact info']
